<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1916-06-21T00:36:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1916-06-21T00:36:00-05:00" n="997" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d997">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.11/7812</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Special Representative <persName type="from">Rodgers</persName> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                    State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Mexico City</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-06-20T23:00:00-06:36">
                                    <hi rend="italic">June 20, 1916, 11 p.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>163. Arranged for transportation Americans to Vera Cruz Thursday,
                            authorities giving full consent. Cars and motive power from Pachuca
                            mines will be used and protection promised. Reporting further this
                            subject to-morrow.</p>
                        <pb facs="0770" n="694" xml:id="pg_694"/>
                        <p>Assured, in the event of hostilities, our associates and myself will be
                            given safe conduct to coast or border. American newspaper correspondents
                            will remain and go with me if that necessity occurs. Please announce
                            this.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Rodgers</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>